            "title": "Coinbase CEO sees Visa (NYSE: V) and Mastercard (NYSE: MA) as partners, not competitors in crypto payments industry.",
            "id": "7b32d1e0-650b-4908-b431-a88e6a1e374c",
            "description": "CEO Brian Armstrong of Coinbase Global Inc. (NASDAQ: COIN) expressed the company's perspective on Visa Inc. (NYSE: V) and Mastercard Inc. (NYSE: MA), considering them as partners rather than competitors in the cryptocurrency-powered payments industry. The CEO shared insights during Coinbase's second-quarter earnings call, responding to queries about potential competition with the fintech giants by stating they do not plan to establish an alternative network. Armstrong highlighted the collaboration with Visa and Mastercard on various card offerings and emphasized their active involvement in stablecoins and cryptocurrency projects. He underscored the partnerships and joint initiatives in the evolving crypto landscape.",
            "link": "https://www.markets.news/headlines/7b32d1e0-650b-4908-b431-a88e6a1e374c",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-01 11:59:05",
            "source": "unusualwhales",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
